00087 #define genAlt(Name, Type, Member) \
00088     dumpf("#define " #Name " 0x%lx\n", OFFSET(Type, Member))
00089 
00090 #define genCom(Comment)        \
00091     dumpf("\n");               \
00092     dumpf("//\n");             \
00093     dumpf("// " Comment "\n"); \
00094     dumpf("//\n");             \

00137 //
00138 // This routine returns the bit number right to left of a field.
00139 //
00140 
00141 LONG
00142 t (
00143     IN ULONG z
00144     )
00145 
00146 {
00147     LONG i;
00148 
00149     for (i = 0; i < 32; i += 1) {
00150         if ((z >> i) & 1) {
00151             break;
00152         }
00153     }
00154     return i;
00155 }
